data.text: @AnneStull @rlecwag Oh that stinks. I hope you feel better. So far just a sore injection arm. Tomorrow will be the real test.
@rlecwag @wendyinthedena Update: I now have a fever. Hope you ladies are feeling good ❤️
@rlecwag @wendyinthedena I’m really tired and have minor body aches. Injection arm is sore, but nothing major. Glad you’re feeling okay!
@AnneStull @wendyinthedena How is everyone feeling today?  My side effects were minimal, just really tired.
@AnneStull @wendyinthedena I’m 7 hours in and same.  Been taking emergenC since after the first shot after hearing from people who said it really helped.  Here’s hoping. 🤞
@wendyinthedena @rlecwag I’m 9 hours in and still only a sore arm. I hear all the fun stuff will start tomorrow 😂
@AnneStull @rlecwag I get my 2nd one tomorrow morning. I’ve never been more excited to get a needle

@rlecwag Congrats!  We need your help to get everyone vaccinated. Please share a photo or video to inspire others to get vaccinated - tag it and we’ll RT #GetTheVax #f2fa
 Thanks!  Get #face2face with those you love. Get back to what inspires you. Get #vaccinated
@rlecwag Got my second today as well. My son got his first. #DoingOurPart
